msgstr "Pré-requisitos"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://azure.microsoft.com[An Azure Account].  Free accounts work."
msgstr "https://azure.microsoft.com[Uma conta do Azure]. Contas gratuitas funcionam."

